{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TM6BEUxCmnuKEhwsKRB7Jp","type":"tool_result","content":"  2880→\n  2881→---\n  2882→\n  2883→## Session 92 Retrospective — No-Op #73 (2026-03-28)\n  2884→\n  2885→### Summary\n  2886→\n  2887→No-op session #73. Sprint remains 100% complete (74/74 stories, 17/17 epics). Fixed Ralph's stale-state reversion of stories 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 from `review` back to `done`. Nothing else.\n  2888→\n  2889→### Cost Analysis\n  2890→\n  2891→- **Total project spend:** $801.48 across 5,847 API calls\n  2892→- **Average cost per story:** $3.78 (158 tracked stories)\n  2893→- **Delta since last retro:** +$2.47 and 14 calls for zero productive work\n  2894→- **Estimated waste from 73 no-op sessions:** ~$175-200 (~22-25% of total spend)\n  2895→- **Largest cost categories:** verify phase (53.7%, $430), orchestrator (21.9%, $175) — both inflated by repeated no-op cycles\n  2896→- **\"unknown\" story bucket:** $203.95 (25.4%) — largely no-op session overhead with no story attribution\n  2897→\n  2898→### Root Cause\n  2899→\n  2900→Ralph loads `sprint-state.json` at startup, holds it in memory, and writes it back every iteration. Its in-memory snapshot predates stories 16-5 through 16-8 reaching `done`. Every cycle it overwrites the on-disk state, reverting those 4 stories. The `registerStory` guard prevents phantom stories but not status reversion. This has repeated identically for 73 consecutive sessions.\n  2901→\n  2902→### Action Item\n  2903→\n  2904→**STOP RALPH.** The sprint has been 100% complete since session 30. Seventy-three consecutive sessions have burned ~$175-200 in API costs doing nothing but fixing the same 4-story state corruption. No per-session fix can resolve this — the loop process must be killed. If Ralph is ever restarted, the state snapshot mechanism needs a redesign that either (a) never downgrades a story from `done`, or (b) re-reads disk state before each write.\n  2905→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_014UrEJtrCUoYgtvGyvyPxvW","session_id":"c5951ad8-792a-4006-ad9a-6c1a026c2d6f","uuid":"863e882e-e48a-4940-8091-02c29c86453f","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:21:20.853Z"}
